    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Microsoft Word is a powerful word processing application that helps you create, edit, and format documents. This lesson covers the essential features and interface elements you need to get started with Word."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Learning Objectives"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "Navigate the Word interface confidently",
          "Create and edit documents effectively",
          "Apply basic formatting techniques",
          "Use keyboard shortcuts for efficiency",
          "Save and manage Word files"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Getting Started with Word"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Opening Word"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "There are several ways to open Microsoft Word depending on your setup and preferences."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "**From Start Menu**: Click the **Start** button and search for **Word**",
          "**From Desktop**: Double-click the Word icon",
          "**From Office.com**: Visit [office.com](https://office.com) and launch Word Online"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Understanding the Interface"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Familiarize yourself with the main components of the Word interface to work efficiently."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": {
        "headers": ["Component", "Description"],
        "rows": [
          ["**Ribbon**", "Tabs with commands organized by function"],
          ["**Quick Access Toolbar**", "Customizable toolbar for frequently used commands"],
          ["**Document Area**", "Main workspace for typing and editing"],
          ["**Status Bar**", "Displays document info and zoom controls"],
          ["**Navigation Pane**", "Helps navigate through document sections"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Basic Text Operations"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Typing and Editing"
